Blockchain-Based Tutoring Trust System
A decentralized platform leveraging blockchain technology to solve trust and transparency issues in the tutoring industry, built on Stacks blockchain.
Problem Statement
The tutoring industry faces several critical challenges:
Trust Verification: Families struggle to find reliable tutors with verifiable credentials and reviews
Payment Security: Lack of secure, transparent payment mechanisms
Review Authenticity: Traditional platforms suffer from unverified or manipulated reviews
Payment Protection: No clear payment protection mechanisms for both tutors and students
Solution
Our platform leverages blockchain technology to create a transparent, secure tutoring ecosystem:
Core Features
Blockchain-Verified Reviews: Immutable review system using BNS-V2 smart contracts
Smart Contract Payments: Secure payment processing with automatic escrow
Trust Score Algorithm: Dynamic trust scoring based on transaction analysis
Transparent History: Complete visibility of tutor-student interactions